data.description: Discover the allure of this 1600 sq ft traditional ranch home in Norfolk, Virginia. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, the residence embodies classic charm. The exterior showcases an inviting front porch and a harmonious blend of earthy tones. Inside, an open floor plan connects the living spaces, accentuating details like crown molding and laminate floors. Abundant natural light graces the interior through large windows. The home's three bedrooms offer comfort, and the master bedroom features an ensuite bath. The backyard retreat is adorned with lush landscaping and a patio. This Norfolk gem seamlessly combines timeless design with modern functionality.
